br />\n到單腳嗰陣身體點樣轉移重心令你唔會失平衡<br />\nfing手要點fing先平衡到個身<br />\n對眼要點郁先可以令自己睇到嘅野唔會上下郁<br />\n之類之類<br />\n每行到一個新環境/新地形就再做一次<br />\n自己被人推嗰陣留意自己啲手腳點郁嚟保持平衡<br />\n跌倒之後手腳同身點郁先企得幾身<br />\n<br />\n真係要寫個咁嘅programme/ 咁樣搖控？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:31:07.000Z","msg":"小學生放假,以為好似人咁有自己思考先叫ai。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"港大都買左第一代Atlas，但比賽行左一步就訓低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:11:51.000Z","msg":"我都記得，program 要自己搞，點知hku 會咁jack<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f630ecd68340f2d2e19f62e38fab1c5ffd737c","tid":560912,"uid":7237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cb39217ed3b70e7300a07f2b0110223cacaa8ca6","tid":560912,"uid":33174,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e2e3e6be6f3807e8cc6fa4937338723f9c60eee0","tid":560912,"uid":169310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25c17147396bef16c8ce2fa8d184e30ec3aeef50","tid":560912,"uid":10890,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T18:23:07.000Z","msg":"唔係呼吸聲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係摩打轉嘅聲嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"呼吸聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打應該係文科仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T03:56:43.000Z","msg":"未必 似戇鳩仔多啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"究竟要幾戇鳩先講得出係呼吸聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37aa7d7f9b0e99ad3e0ecaf38399b6ff1d0adc14","tid":560912,"uid":102872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a4427f1ec0715dab240a1696050c117132c04fa","tid":560912,"uid":18167,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T02:41:51.000Z","msg":"美帝科技永遠都有片有圖睇<br />\n中國科技就永遠都純文字討論 <img src=\"/